        <abstract> 
<p>C. Nägeli’s long letter on his four years of work on <hi rend="italic">Hieracium</hi> appears to be valuable. Nägeli wants a set of British forms in exchange for German ones.</p>  
<p>Sends note on a new genus of Umbelliferae (<hi rend="italic">Drusa</hi>) in Canaries; speculates on origin.</p> 
        </abstract>
